"In different regions, people celebrate festivals in various ways. Meizu Calendar collects fun celebrations from around the globe for your amusement. Can you imagine that Egyptians shed tears on Thanksgiving, while over a hundred monkeys enjoy a lush feast to their content? Plus, special tips are provided to help you find a date by Singles' Day, plan a romantic Valentine's Day, and more.
By subscribing to Festival Pedia, you can get timely, interesting, and useful festival information right on the Calendar homepage."
